    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333hp through six individual throttle bodies. This example retains its mechanical integrity with a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis remains balanced thanks to a well-sorted suspension geometry, and the subframe has been inspected for structural rigidity. Recent service includes a VANOS system refresh and valve adjustment to ensure the high-revving valvetrain operates within factory tolerances. While showing minor signs of road use consistent with its age, the performance envelope remains fully intact, offering a visceral analog experience.",
