    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a reliable, well-maintained machine that bridges the gap between a daily commuter and a pride-of-ownership prize. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss finish, accented by clean body lines; while you might find the occasional minor stone chip consistent with careful highway driving, there are no significant blemishes or unsightly dents. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean and smoke-free. The upholstery is firm and supportive, showing only light softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster, and all interior electronics\u2014from the premium sound system to the dual-zone climate control\u2014operate flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is in its prime. The engine starts instantly and idles smoothly, benefiting from a documented history of synthetic oil changes and preventative maintenance. The brakes are sharp, the tires have ample tread remaining, and the transmission delivers crisp, confident shifts. It has been recently detailed and inspected, making it a turn-key option for its next owner. This is an honest, solid vehicle that has been cared for by an attentive owner.",
